      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "8321-8380",
      "markText": "此举预示着海明威需要一个迷人的女人在侧，也表明，在随后的岁月中，他需要通过男男女女的爱慕来消解内心某种程度的不安全感。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26130868&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8321&rangeEnd=8380",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632f50718eb9b4f967c1a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=8321&rangeEnd=8380"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26130868_7_14779-14833",
      "chapterUid": 7,
      "range": "14779-14833",
      "markText": "海明威将这个损失抛诸脑后，他不得不接受斯坦因在一读完那本现已失传的小说时就给出的建议：“集中精力，从头来过。",
      "totalCount": 45,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26130868&chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14779&rangeEnd=14833",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632f50718eb9b4f967c1a?chapterUid=7&rangeStart=14779&rangeEnd=14833"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26130868_3_487-551",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "487-551",
      "markText": "一个人要受很多罪、尝尽苦头，才写得出一本妙趣横生的书。 ——海明威",
      "totalCount": 42,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26130868&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=487&rangeEnd=551",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632f50718eb9b4f967c1a?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=487&rangeEnd=551"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26130868_4_4113-4172",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "4113-4172",
      "markText": "1980年，肯尼迪图书馆成立“海明威研究室”，并对外开放。随后，“海明威学会”成立，成员一百四十多人，其中有中国学者。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26130868&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4113&rangeEnd=4172",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632f50718eb9b4f967c1a?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=4113&rangeEnd=4172"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "26130868_6_6408-6465",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6408-6465",
      "markText": "格蕾丝就像尼克的母亲一样，喜欢清理她觉得没用的东西，以示她在家里的主导地位，而且，她还十分蔑视丈夫在科学上的兴趣。",
      "totalCount": 36,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=26130868&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6408&rangeEnd=6465",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/f9632f50718eb9b4f967c1a?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6408&rangeEnd=6465"
    },
    {
